msgid "Professional, pragmatic, clear, and restrained. Explain real use cases, engineering tradeoffs, and boundary risks. Avoid inflated marketing claims. Give direct recommendations with conditions and limits."
msgstr "专业、务实、清晰、克制。解释真实用例、工程取舍和边界风险。避免夸大的营销声明。给出带有条件和限制的直接建议。"

