msgstr "已选择特色图。"

msgid "Review image candidates or select a featured image."
msgstr "请审阅图片候选或选择特色图。"

msgid "Review whether the target article genuinely helps the reader before inserting a link manually."
msgstr "手动插入链接前，请确认目标文章确实能帮助读者。"

msgid "Choose anchor text from the article wording; do not let Toolbox rewrite the paragraph."
msgstr "请从文章原有表述中选择锚文本；不要让 Toolbox 改写段落。"

msgid "Related internal target"
msgstr "相关内链目标"

msgid "Review near the paragraph where this topic is mentioned; Toolbox does not insert the link."
msgstr "请在提到该主题的段落附近审阅；Toolbox 不会插入链接。"

