msgstr "归档页和分享场景所需摘要已填写。"

msgid "Run summary suggestions before publishing if the excerpt is empty."
msgstr "如果摘要为空，请在发布前运行摘要建议。"

msgid "At least one category is selected."
msgstr "已选择至少一个分类。"

msgid "Review category suggestions before publishing."
