msgstr "图片优化审核"

msgid "Preview selected images before submitting an optimization request."
msgstr "提交优化申请前，先预览所选图片。"

msgid "Batch work starts from selected media-library images or a bounded sample. Nothing is written automatically."
msgstr "批量任务从所选媒体库图片或有限样本开始。不会自动写入任何内容。"

msgid "Selected attachment IDs"
msgstr "已选附件 ID"

msgid "Optional: 12, 34, 56"
msgstr "可选：12, 34, 56"

msgid "Use the media library bulk action to prefill this field, or leave it empty to scan by range."
msgstr "可通过媒体库批量操作预填此字段，也可以留空后按范围扫描。"

msgid "Batch optimization plan"
msgstr "批量优化计划"

msgid "Choose selected media-library images or a bounded sample, build a review plan, generate selected previews, then submit only selected Core reviews."
msgstr "选择媒体库图片或有限样本，生成审阅计划，生成选中项预览，然后只提交选中项给 Core 审核。"

msgid "Select images"
msgstr "选择图片"

msgid "Preview selected"
msgstr "预览选中项"

msgid "Submit Core review"
msgstr "提交 Core 审核"

msgid "You can start from the media library bulk action, or leave this empty to use the bounded sample below."
msgstr "可以从媒体库批量操作进入，也可以留空后使用下面的有限样本。"

msgid "Review before replacing"
msgstr "替换前先审核"

msgid "This page prepares previews and review requests only. Final media replacement happens later through Core approval and Adapter execution."
msgstr "本页只准备预览和审核申请。最终媒体替换会在 Core 批准并由 Adapter 执行后发生。"

msgid "Need more than one image?"
msgstr "需要处理多张图片？"

msgid "Use the media library bulk action or the Batch Optimize Images tab. This page handles one existing image only."
msgstr "请使用媒体库批量操作或“批量优化图片”标签页。本页只处理一张已有图片。"

msgid "Choose image in media library"
msgstr "去媒体库选择图片"

msgid "Choose an image from Media Library"
msgstr "从媒体库选择图片"

msgid "Open an image attachment, then use Npcink AI to generate an optimization preview."
msgstr "打开一个图片附件，然后使用 Npcink AI 生成优化预览。"

msgid "Start single-image optimization from the media library attachment details panel. Use Batch Image Optimization Review when multiple images or URL repair actions are needed."
msgstr "单张图片优化请从媒体库附件详情面板开始。需要处理多张图片或 URL 修复时，请使用“批量图片优化审核”。"

msgid "Open Media Library"
msgstr "打开媒体库"

msgid "Generate Image Candidate"
msgstr "生成图片候选"

msgid "Generate a Cloud-hosted AI image candidate after operator prompt review, without importing media."
msgstr "在运营者审阅提示词后生成一个 Cloud 托管的 AI 图片候选，不导入媒体。"

msgid "Cloud Web Search"
msgstr "Cloud 网页搜索"

msgid "Run Cloud-managed web search or Zhihu hot-topic atoms for external evidence and topic selection without exposing local provider keys or writing WordPress content."
msgstr "运行 Cloud 托管网页搜索或知乎热点原子，用于外部证据和选题选择，不暴露本地服务商密钥，也不写入 WordPress 内容。"

msgid "Search query or research question."
msgstr "搜索查询或研究问题。"

msgid "Search intent hint such as article_background, fact_check, competitor_research, pricing_snapshot, product_comparison, or general_research."
msgstr "搜索意图提示，例如 article_background、fact_check、competitor_research、pricing_snapshot、product_comparison 或 general_research。"

msgid "Optional Cloud-managed source lane such as zhihu_hot_topics for a cached topic pool, zhihu_research, zhihu_global_search, zhida_simple, zhida_deep, or zhida_deepsearch."
msgstr "可选的 Cloud 托管来源通道，例如用于缓存选题池的 zhihu_hot_topics、zhihu_research、zhihu_global_search、zhida_simple、zhida_deep 或 zhida_deepsearch。"

msgid "Maximum result count requested from Cloud."
msgstr "向 Cloud 请求的最大结果数量。"

msgid "Optional freshness window in days."
msgstr "可选的新鲜度窗口，单位为天。"

msgid "Build Site Knowledge Review Plan"
msgstr "生成站点知识审核计划"

msgid "Build a Core review proposal plan from a Cloud Site Knowledge agent handoff without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "基于 Cloud Site Knowledge agent 交接生成 Core 审核提案计划，不写入 WordPress 内容。"

msgid "Build Nightly Inspection Review Plan"
msgstr "生成夜间巡检审核计划"

msgid "Build a blocked Core review proposal plan from selected Nightly Morning Brief items without writing WordPress content."
msgstr "基于选中的夜间 Morning Brief 条目生成已阻塞的 Core 审核提案计划，不写入 WordPress 内容。"

msgid "Build a one-run Core/Abilities media derivative handoff from Toolbox defaults without writing WordPress media."
msgstr "根据 Toolbox 默认设置生成一次性 Core/Abilities 媒体衍生物交接，不写入 WordPress 媒体。"

msgid "SEO, AEO, GEO, claim boundaries, and technical preview."
msgstr "SEO、AEO、GEO、声明边界和技术预览。"

msgid "Limit what AI can claim and inspect the read-only technical preview exposed to callers."
msgstr "限制 AI 可以声称的内容，并检查暴露给调用方的只读技术预览。"

msgid "Technical preview"
msgstr "技术预览"

msgid "Read-only data"
msgstr "只读数据"

msgid "Batch Fill Missing ALT"
msgstr "批量补全缺失 ALT"

msgid "Find images that need ALT text, review suggestions, then submit selected rows for review."
msgstr "查找需要 ALT 文本的图片，审阅建议，然后将选中行提交审核。"

msgid "Review selected image ALT suggestions before submitting them for review."
msgstr "提交审核前，先审阅选中的图片 ALT 建议。"

msgid "Toolbox only prepares ALT suggestions. Media ALT text changes only after selected rows pass review."
msgstr "Toolbox 只准备 ALT 建议。选中行通过审核后，媒体 ALT 文本才会变更。"

msgid "No media ALT is changed here. Review the rows, then submit selected items for review."
msgstr "这里不会更改媒体 ALT。请先审核各行，再提交选中项审核。"

msgid "Optional one-run crop for common publishing ratios. Cloud returns only a preview; final adoption still requires review."
msgstr "可选的一次性裁剪，用于常见发布比例。Cloud 只返回预览，最终采用仍需审核。"

msgid "Generate a short-lived Cloud preview for one existing media-library image. This check does not submit a review request or write media."
msgstr "为一张已有媒体库图片生成短期 Cloud 预览。此检查不会提交审核请求，也不会写入媒体。"

msgid "Batch image optimization review"
msgstr "批量图片优化审核"

msgid "Use this for multiple existing media-library images. Build a review list first; nothing replaces the original files from this page."
msgstr "用于处理多张已有媒体库图片。请先构建审核列表；本页不会替换原始文件。"

msgid "Choose image source"
msgstr "选择图片来源"

msgid "Build review list"
msgstr "生成审阅列表"

msgid "Generate previews"
msgstr "生成预览"

msgid "Submit optimization request"
msgstr "提交优化申请"

msgid "Use Media Library bulk actions to prefill selected image IDs, or use the source below to build a small sample."
msgstr "可通过媒体库批量操作预填所选图片 ID，也可以使用下面的来源构建小样本。"

msgid "Image source"
msgstr "图片来源"

msgid "This month's images"
msgstr "本月图片"

msgid "Previous month's images"
msgstr "上月图片"

msgid "Custom date range"
msgstr "自定义日期范围"

msgid "Small eligible sample"
msgstr "小范围可处理样本"

msgid "Optimization goal"
msgstr "优化目标"

msgid "Recommended optimization"
msgstr "推荐优化"

msgid "Change file format"
msgstr "转换文件格式"

msgid "Resize large images"
msgstr "缩放大图"

msgid "Add watermark"
msgstr "添加水印"

msgid "Images to review"
msgstr "待审核图片数"

msgid "No original image is replaced here. Review previews first, then submit selected rows. Core may execute automatically only when site policy allows."
msgstr "这里不会替换原图。请先审核预览，再提交所选行。只有站点策略允许时，Core 才会自动执行。"

msgid "Advanced filters and processing options"
msgstr "高级筛选和处理选项"

msgid "Use these only when the review list needs exact media IDs, dates, formats, dimensions, crop, or watermark changes."
msgstr "仅在审核列表需要精确媒体 ID、日期、格式、尺寸、裁剪或水印变更时使用。"

msgid "Selected image IDs"
msgstr "已选图片 ID"

msgid "Submit and execute"
msgstr "提交并执行"

msgid "Submitting and requesting Core execution "
msgstr "正在提交并请求 Core 执行 "

msgid "Core did not return a proposal id for this selected preview."
msgstr "Core 没有为这个已选预览返回提案 ID。"

msgid "Batch submission stopped"
msgstr "批量提交已停止"

msgid "Batch submission finished"
msgstr "批量提交已完成"

msgid "One selected preview failed before all requests were submitted. Review the failed item and retry after revision."
msgstr "某个已选预览在全部请求提交前失败。请检查失败项，修改后重试。"

msgid "Selected previews were submitted. Core executed policy-allowed items and kept blocked items in review."
msgstr "已提交所选预览。Core 已执行策略允许的项目，并将被阻止的项目保留在审核中。"

msgid "Review blocked items in Core before execution."
msgstr "请先在 Core 中审核被阻止的项目，再执行。"

msgid "Review execution records in Core if needed."
msgstr "如有需要，请在 Core 中查看执行记录。"

msgid "If Core policy blocked execution, adjust policy or complete review in Core rather than retrying from Toolbox."
msgstr "如果 Core 策略阻止了执行，请调整策略或在 Core 中完成审核，不要在 Toolbox 中反复重试。"

msgid "Core submission and execution details"
msgstr "Core 提交和执行详情"

msgid "Review the returned plan, then send it to the review system. Final publishing still requires approval outside Toolbox."
msgstr "先审阅返回的计划，再发送到审核系统。最终发布仍需在 Toolbox 外完成审批。"

msgid "Optional review SEO title"
msgstr "可选审核 SEO 标题"

msgid "Optional review SEO description"
msgstr "可选审核 SEO 描述"

msgid "Npcink capability health summary"
msgstr "Npcink 能力健康状态摘要"

msgid "Npcink capability health"
msgstr "Npcink 能力健康状态"

msgid "Read-only workflow status. This is not a generic Abilities Explorer, provider picker, request log, or connector approval surface."
msgstr "只读工作流状态。这里不是通用 Abilities Explorer、Provider 选择器、请求日志或连接器审批界面。"

msgid "Article Audio Candidates"
msgstr "文章音频候选"

msgid "Category and tag suggestions"
msgstr "分类和标签建议"

msgid "Current-article ALT suggestions"
msgstr "当前文章 ALT 建议"

msgid "Comment reply suggestions"
msgstr "评论回复建议"

msgid "Local suggestion context for SEO, AEO, GEO, claims, audience, and tone."
msgstr "用于 SEO、AEO、GEO、声明、受众和语气的本地建议上下文。"

msgid "Search, image, Site Knowledge, hosted AI, and AI image checks use Cloud or a host runtime seam."
msgstr "搜索、图片、Site Knowledge、托管 AI 和 AI 图片检查使用 Cloud 或宿主运行时边界。"

msgid "Default entries"
msgstr "默认入口"

msgid "Npcink workflows"
msgstr "Npcink 工作流"

msgid "Editor defaults stay on preflight, internal links, image candidates, article audio, and governed handoff work."
msgstr "编辑器默认入口保持为发布预检、内链、图片候选、文章音频和受治理交接工作。"

msgid "Route-only compatibility"
msgstr "仅路由兼容"

msgid "%d hidden entries"
msgstr "%d 个隐藏入口"

msgid "Generic AI overlap stays callable for compatibility but is not restored as default Toolbox UI."
msgstr "通用 AI 重叠能力为兼容性保持可调用，但不会恢复为 Toolbox 默认界面。"

msgid "Core handoff boundary"
msgstr "Core 交接边界"

msgid "Write-like outcomes remain Core/Adapter/Abilities handoffs; this summary creates no proposals and writes nothing."
msgstr "类似写入的结果仍然交给 Core/Adapter/Abilities；此摘要不会创建提案，也不会写入任何内容。"
